1. *Nekada* je bio jedan od najvećih gradova u svetu. (Once it was one of the greatest cities in the world.)
2. Ona se *nekada* smejala puno više nego danas. (She used to laugh a lot more than today.)
3. *Nekad* smo se družili skoro svakodnevno. (We used to hang out almost every day.)
4. *Nekadašnji* gradonačelnik je bio poznat po svojoj dobroti. (The former mayor was known for his kindness.)
5. *Nekad* smo živeli u ruralnom delu zemlje. (We used to live in a rural part of the country.)